'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #2548] on 31 August 2000 at 2:23:05 pm'!"Change Set:		longProjMenuDate:			31 August 2000Author:			Bob Arning- change world/new morph/make link to project menu so that it segments when too tall"!!TheWorldMenu methodsFor: 'action' stamp: 'RAA 8/31/2000 14:19'!projectThumbnail	"Offer the user a menu of project names. Attach to the hand a thumbnail of the project the user selects."	| menu projName pr |	menu _ CustomMenu new.	menu 		add: (CurrentProjectRefactoring currentProjectName, ' (current)') 		action: CurrentProjectRefactoring currentProjectName.	menu addLine.	Project allNames do: [:n | menu add: n action: n].	projName _ menu startUpWithCaption: 'Select a project'.	projName ifNotNil:		[(pr _ Project named: projName) 			ifNotNil: [myHand attachMorph: (ProjectViewMorph on: pr)]			ifNil: [self inform: 'can''t seem to find that project']].! !